title: Vikings avoid collapse, Best Week 14 matchups, MJD on Running Backs, Nate Burleson on Demaryius Thomas death
itunes:title: Vikings avoid collapse, Best Week 14 matchups, MJD on Running Backs, Nate Burleson on Demaryius Thomas death
description:
In the latest edition of the Good Morning Football Podcast, hosts Kay Adams, Kyle Brandt, Peter Schrager and Fmr Pro Bowl RB Maurice Jones-Drew examine how the Vikings avoided a monumental collapse on Thursday Night Football. A Mad Minute of Week 14 previews brings Derek Carr heading into Kansas City and Baker Mayfield hosting Lamar Jackson. Kay gives her Top Five Fantasy Football players this week before the crew gives the game their most looking forward to in Week 14. Nate Burleson drops by to discuss the Vikings win and give his thoughts on the shocking news on the passing of fellow WR Demaryius Thomas.

The Good Morning Football Podcast is part of the NFL Podcast Network.
